---
title: Cheesy Cauliflower & Cannellini Bean Gratin with Pear Salad
description: 'Gratin' is the French term for a baked dish with a crispy topping, usually made from breadcrumbs, cheese or a mixture of the two. So Frenchy, so delicious! The star of our gratin is roasted cauliflower, with its tender chunks of bite wrapped up in a thick and creamy sauce. For the topping, we've combined herbed ciabatta and Parmesan – you’re in for a real treat!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheesy-cauliflower-cannellini-bean-gratin-15a1712a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/cheesy-cauliflower-cannellini-bean-gratin-5f18ff962c52a27529676599-33dff2fb.pdf
